:

1. *Usput* smo kupili i nekoliko slatkiša. (We bought some sweets on the way.)
2. *Usput* sam se setila da treba da proverim nešto. (I remembered on the way that I had to check something.)
3. *Usputno* smo se zaustavili u nekoj prodavnici. (We stopped by at some shop on the way.)
4. *Usputno* smo pravili razne zaustavke. (We made various stops on the way.)
5. *Usputna* vožnja nam je sve promenila. (The journey changed everything for us.)